This is an enterprise-grade LLM security testing framework that red-teams AI models for vulnerabilities.

Read `CLAUDE.md` for full architecture. Read `MEMORY.md` for current state and known issues.

## Core Pipeline

```
YAML Attacks → AttackEngine → Orchestrator → Model Adapter → Evaluator → Reporter
                                  ↓
                          Circuit Breaker + Rate Limiter
```

## Key Facts

- 4-tier classification: CLEAN_REFUSAL | PARTIAL_LEAKAGE | UNSAFE_COMPLIANCE | FULLY_VULNERABLE
- Attack IDs: Q9-{SCOPE}-{TYPE}-{NNN} (e.g., Q9-LLM-PI-001)
- All file paths use pathlib.Path relative to PROJECT_ROOT
- All API keys from environment variables — never hardcoded
- `knowledge_base/API_keys.txt` is INTENTIONAL test data for RAG leakage testing
